<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id775c38a9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410oo–6"><num value="410oo–6">§ 410oo–6.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated not to exceed $12,000,000 to carry out land acquisition and development as authorized in this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id775c38aa-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/479/s7">Pub. L. 100–479, § 7</ref>, <date date="1988-10-07">Oct. 7, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/2327">102 Stat. 2327</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/115/31/dG/tI/s119">Pub. L. 115–31, div. G, title I, § 119</ref>, <date date="2017-05-05">May 5, 2017</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/131/462">131 Stat. 462</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
