<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id775c38ad-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2017—<ref href="/us/pl/115/31">Pub. L. 115–31</ref> inserted “land acquisition and development as authorized in” after “carry out”.</p>
